  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to investigate the cost-effectiveness of app-based self-directed ultrasound
      training compared to self-directed training with written handouts on subsequent performance
      on simulated patient cases and theoretical cases.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
